nodes.text: Fromirian roast queg was a gourmet dish.

Vimran Trell, who served as chef aboard the Imperial I-class Star Destroyer Adjudicator, so impressed Moff Renquet with his Fromirian roast queg, that Renquet requested the starship become the flagship of his Sector Fleet. Vimran Trell was in fact a Rebel spy.
